<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link437589" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=437589&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F375064-so-my-mom-recommended-this-book-to-me%2Fanswers%2F437589-it-s-not-a-fast-book">flag</a>
</div>
