<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/312914-who-is-the-antagonist">Who is the antagonist?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_312914'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F177250.The_Mirror_of_Her_Dreams">like</a></span>

