          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;He was too many things at once - a boy, a man, and everything in between - and the differing parts of himself seldom came into balance. She found him attractive in that way. Yet the perception saddened her: she herself wasn't too many things, but too few.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
